parcel.description:
The Official **Hot Tub Boats** Cryptovoxels Outlet!

Hot Tub Boats is Headquartered in Seattle, Wa and we are the the proud designer and inventor of the world's first, well, Hot Tub Boat!

Our free thinking environment allowed us to break the mold and create a revolutionary boat and by merging classic wooden boat design with radical concepts we created a truly one of a kind vessel.
